1481
02:06:23,191 --> 02:06:25,276
Is that the right interpretation?

1482
02:06:25,276 --> 02:06:29,190
Can't be that serious. Most people prefer this one

1483
02:06:30,156 --> 02:06:33,240
Gong Peng, what do you think?

1484
