1524
02:09:37,593 --> 02:09:40,464
Fellow delegates,

1525
02:09:40,555 --> 02:09:44,600
we have a consensus

1526
02:09:44,600 --> 02:09:46,602
that our work here

1527
02:09:46,602 --> 02:09:49,689
